Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.\NAnd how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, they were just thugs!\N- Nothing to do with the syndicate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Dammit, was just a salaried employee...\N...they just wanted money to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...that gave into his temptations.\N- They went to the cops penniless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you caught the criminals, but no\Nclue about the bounty we're really after?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They still use paper just\Nfor all the complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, they're just harassing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,AND, it's a waste\Nof valuable resources!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The e-mail server is going down\Nfrom the sheer number of complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a movement out there\Nto sue our company for damages...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are\Nthe bounty-hunters doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We already have a huge bounty on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amigo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All you bounty-hunters in the{\i0}\N{\i1}Sol system, how are y'all doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once again, it's time for BIG SHOT!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll start with today's hot news!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They apprehended the culprit in{\i0}\N{\i1}the series of recent Gate assaults!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really? The bounty on him was{\i0}\N{\i1}12 million Woolongs, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the weird thing is that{\i0}\N{\i1}20 culprits were apprehended!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apparently, they were all caught in{\i0}\N{\i1}the act, but none were the mastermind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then you don't get the reward{\i0}\N{\i1}unless you find that mastermind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But of course!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh my...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel sorry for all the guys{\i0}\N{\i1}who caught the culprits!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell do these\Nthugs that normally just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...rob convenience stores\Nattack at the Gates?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there are fads in crimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like "Hyperspace Gates are the IN thing\Namong today's fashion-conscious kids!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"That girl won't even\Nlook your way until..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"...you assault at least\None Gate!" or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we trade the\Ninformation that we each have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And split the bounty three ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that\Nstarted all this, saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...that we should research\Nthis case on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You also said that the occasional rivalry\Nbetween comrades would be good for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, did the reward amount\Nmake you lose your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You guys were really\Nkeen on the idea, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we all wanted the\Nbounty to ourselves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this case, all 20 cases{\i0}\N{\i1}were done the same way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of them infiltrated{\i0}\N{\i1}the tollbooth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...deftly attached the hacking unit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and in the exact{\i0}\N{\i1}moment that passing ships...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...access the tollbooth{\i0}\N{\i1}to pay the toll...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...they steal the entire{\i0}\N{\i1}balance from the credit card.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Furthermore, the unit automatically{\i0}\N{\i1}sent the money data that it just stole.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It immediately launders all{\i0}\N{\i1}the funds in a bank on Europa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...making it impossible{\i0}\N{\i1}to track where it went.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the culprits that were caught{\i0}\N{\i1}in the act have nothing in common.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Age, gender, nationality,{\i0}\N{\i1}religion, criminal record...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of it, nobody has any of\Nthe money that they supposedly stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's about all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy that I nabbed said that\Nhe was just following the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...instructions from a manual\Nthat he got through mail-order.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the other culprits are\Nreading the same manual that he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Manual?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"A new criminal support software."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Right now, it's a real bargain.\NFor the low introductory..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"...price of 30,000 Woolongs,\Nyou too can be rich!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy to be a thief nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are people\Nwho want manuals to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And where is this mail-order company?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a store that's only on the\N'net, so I don't know where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the store has already closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The hacking unit that was placed\Non the Gates was something that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...couldn't be made unless you knew\Nabout the Gate system really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The mastermind's likely someone who has\Nsome connection to the Gate Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my hunch, and\NI investigated that front...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The programmers would be fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the guys from the Gate Corporation\Nsuddenly became uncooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if they knew something, but\Ndidn't want us to find out about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess those are the\Nonly clues we have for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a memory cartridge for\Nplaying chess over the 'net.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This piece has one match in its memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And, when you push it,\Nit connects to the 'net.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And this has something to\Ndo with this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe all of this is a game...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, continue playing\Nthat game with the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go talk to the Gate\NCorporation guys once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lessee...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eenie, meenie, miney, moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Another bounty hunter?\NI don't care, send him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's asking about\Na chess-loving programmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Jonathan, were\Nyou another one that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...went through all the\Ntrouble to get nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing isn't that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe we have given\Nout all the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What more are you saying\Nyou would like to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but there is no smoking\Nallowed in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I had something\Nthat I wanted you to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a planned game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys at the Gate Corporation\Nshould know what this means.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, to put a bounty on a mastermind\Nthat we aren't even sure exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...suggests that it's someone you don't\Nwant the police to know about, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Bounty-hunters should just\Nlook for their bounties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are, and\Nwhether or not you used to work for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...the ISSP, but it's better for\Nyou to not make any extra inquiries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure he is kindly\Nescorted out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn this old piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believe our risk is too great.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that gets out to{\i0}\N{\i1}the general public...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am fully aware of our risk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we don't catch him,{\i0}\N{\i1}the situation will just get worse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why is a ghost from{\i0}\N{\i1}50 years ago coming back now...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To think that he gave{\i0}\N{\i1}everyone a chess piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chessmaster Hex...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So it IS a game that he set up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Chessmaster Hex...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No good. This doesn't have anything\Nother than chess data in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they were going\Nto do with such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is no meaning to the content,\Nmaybe the pieces are the message...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spike, I have a name...{\i0}\N{\i1}Can you investigate the guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He might be the mastermind{\i0}\N{\i1}behind this whole thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed's really busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Checkmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...or so you thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fork the king and the rook!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! This is either\Nan idiot or a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this chap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Chessmaster Hex. Estimated\Nto be 98 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A programmer that had been\Ndubbed a genius from his teens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Cosmo-net chess tournaments, he\Ndominated the champion's seat for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He began work on the Hyperspace Gate\Ncontrol program when he was 30...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...and created the central control\Nsystem that all Gates use to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that was his fatal error.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He started to doubt the safety\Nof the Gates he helped create...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...and was against putting\Nthem to practical use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, he was banned\Nfrom the Gate Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since, his whereabouts\Nhave been unknown for 50 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's the mastermind behind\Nour current string of crimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, why is he seeking revenge\N50 years after the fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If we figure out where he is,\Nwe'll know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed's really busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you, quit playing games\Nso much and help out a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed, we want to figure out\Nwhere a guy named Hex is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hex... Hex... The Chessmaster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's who I'm playing\Nchess against right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost at the location we got from\Nthe trace we did on Ed's chess opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys standing by?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he's basically giving\Nus his exact location...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we even trust that\Ntrace in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ya think he'd be in a dump like this?\N- No, I think it was... that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had heard once that there was a place{\i0}\N{\i1}where all the scrapped remains of...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...obsolete Gates were gathered along with{\i0}\N{\i1}scrap metal and abandoned spaceships...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and that there were people{\i0}\N{\i1}that started living there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why the hell do they want{\i0}\N{\i1}to live here of all places?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That area has no nationality,{\i0}\N{\i1}nor a government.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't have to pay taxes,{\i0}\N{\i1}and there are no cops.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see... It's the perfect{\i0}\N{\i1}place to hide yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It might be a trap...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This might be the{\i0}\N{\i1}continuation of the game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens, happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we have air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then there is someone here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yo, Jet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks for leading the way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You... were following\Nus the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tough luck for you, but I have{\i0}\N{\i1}important business with that guy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'll be going ahead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace to the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...and love to my bank account!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chessmaster Hex?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you be a little quieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't joke with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away with\Npretending to be senile!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hand over\Nthe money you stole...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll get a nice\Nhole in your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a big tube you got there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, whatcha doin', Hex?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta hear this. It's my first\Nformidable opponent in quite a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be some player if\Nyou have trouble winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, where's lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are ya saying?\NYou just ate lunch a while back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really, you've lost so much of yer mind...\N- Who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...that all you can do is play chess!\N- Dunno. But you know, this old fogey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Have ya lost it?\N- Like you can speak... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To... To think my life savings\Nare never coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... Goddammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone and everyone, you and\Nthat guy over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is all a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?\NThis old man doesn't seem to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...remember anything about\Nyesterday, let alone 50 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hex is no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we merely have an\Nold man that loves games...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, Hex was riled up for\Nrevenge, and planned this all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He made it so that this incident\Nwould happen 50 years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...during the one moment that the Gate\Nprogram gets automatically updated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even making those that\Nphysically commit the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...hold chess pieces to hint\Nthat it was his doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,However, to that old-timer,\N50 years was too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He went senile,\Nand had completely forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...about the traps that\Nhe himself had set.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it works out better\Nfor you this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now you don't\Nhave to worry about...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...the fundamental defect\Nin the Gates leaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, the price you paid was\Nthat WE learned about that defect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want? Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:21:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Or... are you planning to leak\Nthis information to the press?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave that old guy alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good deal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ed would get lonely if she\Nlost her chess partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're playing that thing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again. Still.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Still?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been playing that\Nthing this whole WEEK?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(737.96,238.47)}{\be1}{\pos(740.96,210.47)}Mate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, newcomer. You seem happy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a really easygoing\Nfellow, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost...
