Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Love... It is to believe everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Love... It is the heart\Nthat provides for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... was that what\Nthe story was about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.35,0:24:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Love... It is the heart\Nthat accepts everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.65,0:24:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this is getting fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitney... You loved me that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.86,0:24:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can't trust\Nthe previews on this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A romantic love story\Nfor all you lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.16,0:24:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: My Funny Valentine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.70,0:24:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.49,0:24:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a lie. A lie.
